Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:03.65,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday's me to today's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:07.57,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"You will lose your memory every thirteen hours."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:12.08,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"It's the result of a traffic accident that happened four years ago."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:15.70,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry to tell you that you also lost your left eye."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:19.97,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Please accept what has happened is real."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.39,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Here, I will write down what you need to know for you to live on."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:31.98,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"First, please, without fail, read this diary every morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.48,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"This is your memory."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.98,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything of yours is here."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:42.32,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Second, please make sure to write in the diary."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:45.80,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"What you did that day, the conversations you had, medical records, etc."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:49.08,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Please write them down as accurately as you can."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:39.02,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"Third, if possible, please avoid coming into contact with strangers."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:46.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"Due to this handicap, you might have a hard time or might trouble the person you've met."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.82,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"In case you meet someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:53.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,please write down that person's exact characteristics and information in the diary."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.45,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,At first,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:06.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote down that you're a small, older guy in a school uniform, who came to the station around three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Older?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:13.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because for me, time stopped four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:15.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you wore plain clothes on holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:23.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,or if I met you before three o'clock, I wouldn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.66,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry. This is a diary after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:45.04,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen hours. That's the number of hours you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:51.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I remember from when I get up at seven o'clock in the morning until eight o'clock in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:57.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But, after that, an hour of my memories disappears as each hour passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:03.98,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,At twelve o'clock midnight, my memories from before eleven o'clock in the morning will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And then at seven o'clock the next morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:12.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,my memories before six o'clock, the previous evening, will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, when you get up in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have forgotten all about your encounter with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:22.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:28.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think back upon things that are important to me. Many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:34.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I manage to recall them, I'm able to remember them for the next thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,At nine o'clock in the evening, before I go to sleep, I read the dairy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,and think back upon the things that are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:47.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I'm able to remember them even the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I had fun with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.65,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,and the fact that I have a memory defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:59.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I live a peaceful life right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:04.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't go to school, and since I don't have anyone whom I can call a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really doing nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:12.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I space out at the station, then I won't have anything I need to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.18,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a worthless life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I let go of everything, life will be very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:23.85,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true{\fscx300}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.18,Main2,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:31.19,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, if I can, my goal is to live a life without troubling others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,However, that's difficult as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:38.20,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm alive, I {i}will{/i} trouble someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:43.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll heartlessly forget that I troubled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.24,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.75,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:51.08,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.13,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.17,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back. Dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:05.08,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Renji, you got the career interest survey, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.38,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the other mothers talking about it in cooking class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:14.19,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty early. You're still a first-year student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.19,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.38,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,What will you write down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.41,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.41,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you just write down what you want to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,If I could decide, I wouldn't be stressed over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:31.32,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there's something I'd like you to deliver to Kuze-san after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san is back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:34.85,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:39.43,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,The pot on the stove is his share. Bring it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:40.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:44.79,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.61,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:55.67,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're as short as ever. Have you been eating properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:59.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,After three months, is that the first thing you've got to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.68,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that my usual share?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My mom told you to enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.41,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I accept it gratefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:08.48,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what today's dish is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:11.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:18.13,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you don't mind that there's a girl on my bed who's wearing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:24.15,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I do, so forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.85,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.64,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Worrying over something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.94,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.94,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.94,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll visit your place with a souvenir next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:42.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,After you're finished with the pot, please leave it in front of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.24,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:46.11,Main,Shuichi,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Renji. Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.16,Main,Sumire,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.16,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,The same peaceful day as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:02.92,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I feel that way because I remember my usual life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.22,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy to see Kuze-san yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.93,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I remember Kuze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.77,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But for Chihiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:19.03,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,both the day she lived and the people she met disappear from her memory after thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:26.24,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see Chihiro simply because I wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:35.15,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But Chihiro has to be mentally prepared to meet a stranger like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.92,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she feels anxious and scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.46,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.71,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.22,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:50.65,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right for me to go and see Chihiro with such an irresponsible attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.01,MainF,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\2a&Hff\fad(300,0)}If you want to stay by Chihiro's side, you have to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:58.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Am I just being half-hearted about Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be there today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.99,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell you a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.66,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:23.30,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Every day I think about how I can disappear without troubling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.10,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I've given up on that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:31.21,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:34.25,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of being afraid will simply disappear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:34.93,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.05,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:42.54,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm truly afraid of is not the disappearance of my own memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:46.02,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,but disappearing from the memories of everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:52.66,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Surprisingly, I'm quite a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A joke...{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0} eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:55.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A joke... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:10:00.67,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there something I can do for Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:05.32,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Something that a knight can do to protect his princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.42,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Something that will make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.39,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:10.51,MainF,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.72,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to write stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:16.43,MainF,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a single story,\NI want to complete one as my current self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.20,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,How come you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.63,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:43.67,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro caught a cold. "Since I couldn't come here today, I'm sorry," she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.30,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.69,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an ordinary cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:52.14,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,To be safe, she's forbidden to go out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.39,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I...{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0} see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.31,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I... see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.26,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.81,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You two made a promise, right? "See you tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.81,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro was here till midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:15.15,bw,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for her memory loss, Chihiro makes sure that she keeps that kind of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:23.67,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,To her, "see you tomorrow" is an important promise that connects the her of that day to the her of a different day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.83,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:30.08,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I came to pick her up, she told me she had made a promise with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.08,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,How stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:39.48,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Since Chihiro cannot confirm her own existence, she listens to everything people tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.65,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she still has some human qualities left in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.05,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I... {\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0}didn't even realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I... didn't even realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.55,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:58.07,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro's inflexibility about her common sense just means I'm not qualified to be her guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:00.95,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.87,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.34,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:18.80,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yo. Practicing by yourself this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.44,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. Everyone is too slow, so I left them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Aside from that, what's wrong? You're up so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:30.60,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I finished the script through sheer willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.40,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just brought it to the editing department.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:37.07,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I fell asleep, I wouldn't be able to wake up, so I thought I'd head straight to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.90,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of wind is blowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.62,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is it going to rain too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.83,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guarantee I'll be awake during class though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:47.04,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:49.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You drank all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I commend you for your solo efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:59.22,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:11.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.00,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mad. It's just a cute prank that's done all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.17,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you only cover the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.95,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Normal is no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.50,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill me for a reason like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:34.00,bw,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:35.99,bw,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Because, if you weren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:43.57,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,The lock to such a wonderful hiding place couldn't be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:48.01,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, will you give that to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:48.89,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important souvenir my elder sister gave me as congratulations for being admitted to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:56.19,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Even a duplicate key is fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:59.82,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm gonna share my precious space, where I can be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:05.87,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hirono-kun. What about your job today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:11.98,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't finish your script soon, will your editor beat you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't come to school under such circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:20.42,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second. Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.69,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere that's not{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0} h-e-r-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.46,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere that's not h-{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0}e-r-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.31,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere that's not h-e-{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0}r-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere that's not h-e-r-{\1a&HFF&\bord0\shad0}e.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.55,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,{\2a&Hff\fad(0,1000)}Somewhere that's not h-e-r-e.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.39,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it looks ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.51,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "ordinary"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:38.28,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it came out of a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.95,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of film is commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.57,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We {i}made{/i} it to look ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.45,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It looks too much like Impressionism if we combine your shots together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.83,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:55.15,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Works that are too individualistic won't be considered for the special prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:59.61,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you plan to go after a high-ranking prize, a solid production will work better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.09,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:08.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, even simply taking a walk in Otawa is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been living here forever, so I'm tired of seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:16.67,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a difference in the scenery you usually see when two people walk together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:23.67,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This Otawa town had ordinary Japanese scenery before as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.41,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was all wiped out by the earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:30.45,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was also burned to ashes during the war. What an unlucky town.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.74,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:36.83,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,They built a town that was completely different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:44.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hold back. I have money with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:47.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed up all night, so I can't eat that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.80,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,The weather is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:54.88,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd feel like attending class on a day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.53,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You skip school regardless of the weather, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:15:59.46,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.81,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:03.06,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.32,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,The town is way more interesting than lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.67,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:13.49,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate school. I just hate being bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.37,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, isn't it better to choose the interesting one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:21.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I shouldn't be the one to say so, it's bad not to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:26.15,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If the world was restrained to common sense, life wouldn't be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:30.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You should also do things that you think you'd enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.34,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.73,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:39.15,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai, what are you doing at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.23,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.66,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.76,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,For my supply of shoujo manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:49.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You really like manga, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:52.00,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:56.04,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. She's my kouhai, Hayama Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.25,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.68,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's my classmate, Miyamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:03.08,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura... erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.08,Main2,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.77,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:10.52,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I order you to call me "Miyako" from this very moment on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:18.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is thoroughly scarred because you forgot my name so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what I should do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.65,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.18,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.41,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:32.78,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's weird to call your girlfriend by her last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.93,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro-senpai is such a shy guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.14,0:17:39.33,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:46.34,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if you got a girlfriend, the available Kei-senpai would be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:50.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,How come even Kei is now my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.69,Main,Mizuki,0000,0000,0000,,You got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.48,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, she's not my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:01.40,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:05.10,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel, but try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.90,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone worked hard to win at this Cinema Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.69,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You guys always talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.30,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing you care about is the evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.49,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You should stick to what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.65,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:22.38,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sticking to what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.25,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:24.50,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,"No idea"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:28.18,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I'm bored lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.83,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking through the finder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.39,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.38,bw,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.01,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.51,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:42.61,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:48.78,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I don't understand you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.23,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.03,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fill out the notice that I'm leaving the club, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.82,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.41,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,The site of the earthquake, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.79,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:11.42,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:18.17,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to look back at the wreckage of a past that's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.78,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I only look forward all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:26.22,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Aren't you unable to see what you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.98,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:32.06,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,But I decided what I wanted to do a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.06,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.57,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I take the shots I want to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.86,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.36,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to take is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:42.45,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,A dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:54.28,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,The cold is nothing serious, but Himura-san won't let me go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.34,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even though, I want to go see Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:00.17,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You have to listen to what Himura-san tells you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:02.85,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,If you get worse, it'll be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.19,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.43,0:20:14.52,MainT,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-kun, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:19.97,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:24.26,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yawn while watching someone practicing. It's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:27.24,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a different timetable than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.50,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Humans should sleep at night and wake up in the morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:34.00,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Manga artists are creatures who really live outside the confines of human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.49,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:39.30,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to talk to me about this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.52,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You skipped school yesterday, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:48.94,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. My body couldn't stand it after staying up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I went home to sleep in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.66,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:58.05,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You were with Miyamura-senpai, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.11,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Mizuki. You ran into her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:04.11,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You know Miyamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,She's famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:10.26,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You're about the only one who doesn't know, since you don't come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:16.72,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's pretty, the guys always talk about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.45,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,She's a habitual school-skipper,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.45,0:21:23.38,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,and even when she attends class once in a while, she completely ignores what the teacher says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:25.80,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,When she's called on, she doesn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.92,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Your attendance record is already dangerously bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.92,0:21:34.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't know the circumstances, yet she just took you out as she liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.94,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:41.61,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bad-mouthing someone you don't really know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:46.20,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Miyamura-senpai well, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.26,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,T-The first time we met was Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:52.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been a month yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:56.21,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:03.98,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you broke your promise to me because you met Miyamura-senpai?
